        <Parent_String>grinding stones [300263933], culinary mills [300201099], food mills, grinders and presses [300201096], culinary equipment for preparing and cooking food [300199784], culinary equipment [300199765], equipment by context [300239170], equipment [300122241], Tools and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300022238], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
